    <title metal:fill-slot="title">About Malone</title>

<body>
<div metal:fill-slot="main">

    <h1>Welcome to Malone!</h1>
    <p class="discreet">
        Malone is a system for reporting bugs in software. Please choose a link
        below to get started.
    </p>

    <ul>
        <!--<li><a href="+about">About Malone</a></li>-->
        <li><a href="bugs/+new">File a Bug</a> - report a bug in some software you're using</li>
        <li><a href="bugs">Search/View Bugs</a> - view or search bugs that have already been reported</li>
        <li><a href="/foaf/people/+new">Join</a> - create a new user account</li>
    </ul>

</div>
</body>
